      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，这三步都是5分、5分、1分的体验评分。用户发消息和AI回复都很顺畅，但token更新是后台静默做的，用户无感知，所以给1分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User write message",
        "Ai assistant answer",
        "Tokens quantity update",
        "5",
        "1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
