    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第一块我先画好。然后第二块\"Payment flow\"——token耗尽后前端提示，用户点击充值入口，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
