      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到你刚才说\"后端更新token\"，但第一块里已经有个\"Tokens quantity update\"了。第二块末尾的\"Tokens for user update\"是同一个东西吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
